@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_odsskk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.47 / v1 + 0.15)))
    tmp = (v0 / ((v2 + 0.35 / tmp + 0.31) - 0.43))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.23 + v1 + 0.44)))
    data[tid] = v0
